News.headline: Essex Senior Cup: Dagenham and Redbridge v Heybridge Swifts
News.page_title: Essex Senior Cup: Dagenham and Redbridge v Heybridge Swifts
News.URL_keywords: Essex Senior Cup: Dagenham and Redbridge v Heybridge Swifts
News.short_description: The Daggers have been drawn at home to Heybridge Swifts in the fourth round of the Essex Senior Cup.
News.description:
The tie will take place on Tuesday 6th December and kick-off will be at 7:45pm. 

Ticket prices:
Adults: £6.00 
Concessions/Juniors: £3.00 

Tickets for the game will be cash on the turnstiles.
